{"tid":809022,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"畢·雷諾士死咗","createTime":"2018-09-06T22:29:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T22:29:45.000Z","uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d54ded6e6d826adf5b109f1af372ad5088e42d58","tid":809022,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T22:29:45.000Z","msg":"RIP <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Smokey and the Bandit star Burt Reynolds dies from heart attack, aged 82</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/09/06/20/4FCC06C500000578-6140349-image-a-18_1536261389988.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F09%2F06%2F20%2F4FCC06C500000578-6140349-image-a-18_1536261389988.jpg&h=dba4c88b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Reynolds was best known for his roles in 1972's Deliverance, 1977's Smokey and the Bandit (pictured) and 1997's Boogie Nights - the last of which earned him an Oscar nomination.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/09/06/20/4FCC060600000578-6140349-image-a-14_1536261351994.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F09%2F06%2F20%2F4FCC060600000578-6140349-image-a-14_1536261351994.jpg&h=8d82d899&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n The actor, pictured on Smokey and the Bandit with the 'one that got away' as ex-girlfriend Sally Field, suffered a cardiac arrest Thursday morning <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/09/06/20/4FCC10EC00000578-6140349-image-m-20_1536261410224.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F09%2F06%2F20%2F4FCC10EC00000578-6140349-image-m-20_1536261410224.jpg&h=9c301889&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n His first big movie breakout role was as Lewis Medlock in box office hit Deliverance  (pictured) in 1972<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/09/06/20/4FCC048300000578-6140349-image-a-17_1536261384821.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F09%2F06%2F20%2F4FCC048300000578-6140349-image-a-17_1536261384821.jpg&h=147c8107&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Reynolds, known for his manly swagger, and was something of a 1970s sex symbol after rising to prominence on TV shows Gunsmoke and Dan August (pictured in an ad for his luxury mail catalog business) <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/09/06/20/4FCC531A00000578-6140349-image-a-26_1536262662143.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F09%2F06%2F20%2F4FCC531A00000578-6140349-image-a-26_1536262662143.jpg&h=10775e79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Reynolds' personal life sometimes overshadowed his movies, with marriages that ended in divorce. He is pictured with second wife Loni Anderson in 1987 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/09/06/20/4FCC530500000578-6140349-image-a-27_1536262675614.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F09%2F06%2F20%2F4FCC530500000578-6140349-image-a-27_1536262675614.jpg&h=be5082f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n He was also married to Judy Carne, his first wife, for three years in the 1960s <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/09/06/21/4FCC6E9200000578-6140349-image-a-68_1536264462256.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F09%2F06%2F21%2F4FCC6E9200000578-6140349-image-a-68_1536264462256.jpg&h=720a45f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Burt Reynolds and Sally Field attend the off-Broadway play &quot;Buried Child'&quot; in New York in 1978. He described Field, then his girlfriend, as the love of his life<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/09/06/20/4FCC10D800000578-6140349-image-m-57_1536263663566.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F09%2F06%2F20%2F4FCC10D800000578-6140349-image-m-57_1536263663566.jpg&h=0c9f176d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Reynolds cited director John Boorman's Oscar-nominated 1972 'Deliverance' (pictured) as his best film<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/09/06/20/4FCC0FD900000578-6140349-He_worked_in_Hollywood_fordecaes_The_star_seen_in_a_1950s_head_s-a-45_1536263092684.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F09%2F06%2F20%2F4FCC0FD900000578-6140349-He_worked_in_Hollywood_fordecaes_The_star_seen_in_a_1950s_head_s-a-45_1536263092684.jpg&h=807b5862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n He worked in Hollywood fordecaes: The star seen in a 1950s head shot<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/09/06/20/4FCC0FC800000578-6140349-Sad_loss_The_actor_went_into_cardiac_arrest_and_died_at_Jupiter_-m-44_1536263086075.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F09%2F06%2F20%2F4FCC0FC800000578-6140349-Sad_loss_The_actor_went_into_cardiac_arrest_and_died_at_Jupiter_-m-44_1536263086075.jpg&h=cf65786e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Sad loss: The actor went into cardiac arrest and died at Jupiter Medical in Florida on Thursday morning, surrounded by his family, manager Erik Kritzer told the Hollywood Reporter; seen in 1977<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/09/06/20/4FCC593300000578-6140349-image-a-47_1536263267934.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F09%2F06%2F20%2F4FCC593300000578-6140349-image-a-47_1536263267934.jpg&h=78465dca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Burt Reynolds and Sally Field in Smokey and the Bandit III. Many of his films were set in the South. He often played a lovable rascal who outwits local authorities as in director Hal Needham's crowd-pleasing action comedy <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/09/06/20/4FCC61D000000578-6140349-image-a-50_1536263300324.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F09%2F06%2F20%2F4FCC61D000000578-6140349-image-a-50_1536263300324.jpg&h=6a19ca4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n In this March 15, 1978 file photo, Reynolds polished his newly unveiled star in the Hollywood Walk of Fame in Los Angeles<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/09/06/20/4FCC06B500000578-6140349-image-a-59_1536263737327.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F09%2F06%2F20%2F4FCC06B500000578-6140349-image-a-59_1536263737327.jpg&h=11fe3de1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Burt Reynolds appeared in Striptease in 1996 - just a year before his Oscar nominated movie Boogie Nights<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/09/06/20/4FCCA1A100000578-6140349-image-a-61_1536263962615.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F09%2F06%2F20%2F4FCCA1A100000578-6140349-image-a-61_1536263962615.jpg&h=f299adc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Reynolds rebounded from a career slump in 1997 with a nomination for a best supporting actor Academy Award for 'Boogie Nights' (pictured)"}]}